---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';

const title = "Franchise Valuation Calculator 2025 | Calculate Franchise Value & ROI";
const description = "Calculate your franchise value with our 2025 ROI analysis calculator. Get accurate franchise valuation using proven industry multiples, territory analysis, and brand premiums.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
    <div class="article-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%); color: white; padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <h1>üè™ Franchise Valuation Calculator 2025</h1>
        <p>Complete ROI Analysis & Value Assessment | Professional Franchise Valuation Services</p>
    </div>

    <div class="calculator-box" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h2>üöÄ Get Your FREE Franchise Valuation Now!</h2>
        <p>Calculate your franchise worth in under 5 minutes using our proven franchise valuation methodology with territory analysis and brand premiums.</p>
        <a href="https://thevaluationgenie.com/" class="cta-button">Calculate My Franchise Value</a>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 15px; opacity: 0.9;">Free estimate ‚Ä¢ Professional $39 reports available</p>
    </div>

    <article>
        <section id="introduction">
            <h2>Introduction to Franchise Valuation</h2>
            <p>Franchise valuation is a specialized field that requires understanding of franchise economics, brand equity, territory rights, and industry-specific metrics. In 2025, the franchise landscape continues evolving with new business models, technology integration, and changing consumer preferences driving valuation premiums.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="roi-analysis">
            <h2>ROI Analysis for Franchises</h2>
            <p>Return on Investment (ROI) analysis is critical for <strong>franchise valuation</strong> because it accounts for the initial franchise investment, ongoing fees, and expected returns. Unlike independent businesses, franchises have unique financial structures requiring specialized analysis.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="faq">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-item" style="background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #3498db; padding: 20px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;">
                <h4>What is the average franchise valuation multiple in 2025?</h4>
                <p>Franchise valuation multiples typically range from 2.5x to 6.5x SDE, depending on the industry, brand strength, territory quality, and operational performance. QSR franchises average 2.5x-4.0x, while healthcare and education franchises can command 4.5x-6.5x multiples.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </article>
</MainLayout>
